{"tid":859802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「一人一post」呼籲星期日一齊去遊行","createTime":"2018-10-12T20:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T03:50:18.000Z","uid":121831,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ef51d23dd8b55492a3a93adcd7f4e347f2717882","tid":859802,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T20:26:46.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔知到時會有幾多人<br />\n即使唔合理我都會同自己講：<br />\n<br />\n我去，大家都會去<br />\n<br />\n就算留言幾多負面言論我都唔會理<br />\n因為喱次阻唔到，香港就乜柒都無。<br />\n<br />\n你未來至少14年既社會福利都會受影響<br />\n所以唔好再覺得同你無關<br />\n<br />\n你唔爭取，第時比大陸狗笑騎騎袋你辛苦賺既錢交既稅，你甘心咩？<br />\n<br />\n你甘心未來交比政府既錢，都繼續斷送比無貢獻無付出既大陸狗咩？<br />\n<br />\n你甘心咩？<br />\n<br />\n10月14日 銅鑼灣東角道 3點為香港剩低既少少希望掙扎<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手一人一post"},{"pid":"e193af47928551bbcdb681f08489a88421c46ece","tid":859802,"uid":186800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T20:34:02.000Z","msg":"就算留言幾多負面言論我都唔會理<br />\n<br />\n呢個咪就係政府既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9c5effcf58361f3e149a24363cca6b2bf601f7","tid":859802,"uid":81732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T00:06:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f74c7461b5584c096a0e306237736ce440314e1d","tid":859802,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb586aa2b0b2a8b5fb650a60db7e90251546d40","tid":859802,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd531fde286c47918bdd734108aeaf68b1221c3","tid":859802,"uid":85799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"唔好再要返工，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係時候要企出黎"},{"pid":"c881eded5e8036653a15e2c6ea79cae5e4849a44","tid":859802,"uid":145530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0